Worldpayments lets you accept a variety of payment types wherever you sell - online or in-person. You can even send invoices with the option to pay by credit card, debit card.
A payment gateway enables transactions between a merchant and customer. When a customer enters their card details on a websites payment page, the payment gateway encrypts the card details to process the card transaction. The card details are first routed to the acquiring banks and then the card schemes. If the customer has sufficient funds in their account, the information is sent back to the merchant informing the customer the payment has been accepted.
Choose the right method to start selling online. Worldpayments is partnered with hundreds of solution providers, so no matter how you sell - from marketplaces or your own online store - you can accept the payment options your customers prefer.
It only takes a few minutes to start adding commerce to your platform. To manage payments, you can set up worlpayments accounts for sellers. Or own the look and feel yourself and have sellers do everything within your platform.
